---
title: Roasted Pork Belly & Char Siu Sauce with Peanut Asian Rice, Pickled Cucumber & Greens
description: Get ready for pork belly! A luxurious dinner is never too far away when slices of tender pork are plated up. In fact, it’s
a guarantee when peanut and corn-tossed rice is added with a pickled cucumber. Combine everything together with a
deliciously dark sauce and there you have it, pork belly with pizazz.
